==Gothic==
===Etymology===
Proto-Germanic ''[[*mathon]]'', derived from Proto-Indo-European ''[[*math-]]'' used in insect names.  Cognates include Old English [[ma镁a]], Old High German [[mado]] (German [[Made]]), Old Saxon [[ma冒o]] (Dutch [[made]]).

